lead_paragraph: Boston College blew a fourth-quarter lead in a loss to Georgia Tech in its season opener in Ireland. In the Eagles' finale, they showed they had learned how to hold on for a victory.

headline.print_headline: Boston College Builds Lead, Holds Off Maryland for 36-30 Win
